exceptions.tactic: intros m l n m' H1 H2.
intros m'' l n m' H1 H2.
intros m'' l' n m' H1 H2.
intros m'' l' n' m' H1 H2.
intros m'' l' n' m''' H1 H2.

exceptions.exn: The reference H2 was not found in the current environment.

original: intros. intros m l n m' H1 H2. destruct H2 as [nm H2]. rewrite <- H1 in H2. destruct nm as [nm1 nm2]. simpl in H2. injection H2 as H3 H4. rewrite <- H3, <- H4. reflexivity.
